WXFORMBUILDER INSTALL FROM SOURCE
---------------------------------

0. Pre-requisites (Ubuntu 12.04 LTS)

sudo apt-get install libwxgtk2.8-0 libwxgtk2.8-dev

1. Download source code

mkdir ~/src/wxformbuider
cd ~/src/wxformbuilder
svn checkout svn://svn.code.sf.net/p/wxformbuilder/code/3.x/trunk head


2. Prepare build files

cd head
./create_build_files4.sh

3. Build

cd build/2.8/gmake
make config=release

4. Test

cd ../../../output/bin/
./wxformbuilder


